title: Microsoft Azure Storage Accounts: Performance
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports metrics regarding performance of monitored
 azure storage accounts.
 You can configure levels for server latency, end-to-end latency
 and availability.
 In order to use this check, you need to onfigure the Azure special agent.

item:
 The name of the resource.

discovery:
 One service is created for each storage account if all required metrics
 (total_SuccessServerLatency, total_SuccessE2ELatency, total_Availability) are given.
